content: Rusty-Gold Cart is a Yaoguai Chief boss fight that you'll go up against toward the end of Chapter 5 in Black Myth: Wukong. This is the final of the Five Element Carts and will allow you to get into the Chapter's Secret Area - Bishui Cave.

Rusty-Gold Cart is a Yaoguai Chief boss fight that you'll go up against toward the end of Chapter 5 in Black Myth: Wukong. This is the final of the Five Element Carts and will allow you to get into the Chapter's Secret Area - Bishui Cave.
